description: Let there be talk! That’s the name of Dean Delray’s hit podcast and what we’re doing on this one too. We’re talking everything from French bulldogs to puppy presidents, if snoring as a fetish to properly ending TV shows. Here’s five words to describe this episode: don’t jump the shark now.
